    java.io.Serializable
    public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Defines a The notion of Person to the System. This person has the following attributes:
    1. Name
    2. Password
    3. Departament
    4. Address
    5. PhoneNumber
    6. CC number
    7. Type
    8. CC Validity
